data.description: First time on the market!  This classic Gambrel home with fantastic curb appeal is cute as a button! Situated on just over an acre in a quaint & quiet neighborhood close to Forebay Lake, shopping, restaurants and more. Featuring updated kitchen & baths, radiant heat in ceilings, bonus rooms, workshop off garage, several storage sheds, custom carport, RV Parking w/ electric hookup, High-Speed X-Finity Internet, hard wired Generac system covered by metal shed and many other extras! Relax on the deck, tinker away in the workshop, get dirty in the garden. There's so much here to enjoy + there's plenty of room to use your imagination and make it your own. The perfect place to settle down roots & call home!
